                                double percentOccurrance,

Creates a statistics object for a particular link type.

Parameters:
objFrom - the type of the object(s) at the begining of the link
objTo - the type of the object(s) at the end of the link
linkType - the type of the link
percentOccurrance - the percent of links of this type which connect object of type objFrom to object of type objTo
ctOccurrance - the number of links of this type which connect objects of type objFrom to objects of type objTo
